---
title: Sweet Chilli King Prawn & Halloumi Loaded Flatbreads with Bell Pepper, Chips and Tomato Salad
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Sweet Chilli King Prawn and Halloumi Loaded Flatbreads are perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner.
